     fhir:Narrative.status [ fhir:value "extensions" ] ;
     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: CapabilityStatement CapabilityStatement-ems-core-server</b></p><a name=\"CapabilityStatement-ems-core-server\"> </a><a name=\"hcCapabilityStatement-ems-core-server\"> </a><h2 id=\"title\">EMS Core Server Capability Statement</h2><ul><li>Implementation Guide Version: 0.2.0 </li><li>FHIR Version: 4.0.1 </li><li>Supported Formats: <code>json</code>, <code>xml</code></li><li>Published on: 2026-03-14 </li><li>Published by: fhirEMSCore Research Project (AI-Generated — Unofficial) </li></ul><blockquote class=\"impl-note\"><p><strong>Note to Implementers: FHIR Capabilities</strong></p><p>Any FHIR capability may be 'allowed' by the system unless explicitly marked as 'SHALL NOT'. A few items are marked as MAY in the Implementation Guide to highlight their potential relevance to the use case.</p></blockquote><h3 id=\"shallIGs\">SHALL Support the Following Implementation Guides</h3><ul><li><a href=\"index.html\">https://fhirems.github.io/fhirEMSCoreIG/ImplementationGuide/fhirems.emscore</a></li><li><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/us/core/STU6.1/ImplementationGuide-hl7.fhir.us.core.html\">http://hl7.org/fhir/us/core/ImplementationGuide/hl7.fhir.us.core</a></li></ul><h2 id=\"rest\">FHIR RESTful Capabilities</h2><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h3 id=\"mode1\" class=\"panel-title\">Mode: <code>server</code></h3></div><div class=\"panel-body\"><div><p>EMS PCR Server. Supports creation and retrieval of EMS Patient Care Report resources.</p>\n</div></div></div><h3 id=\"resourcesCap1\">Capabilities by Resource/Profile</h3><h4 id=\"resourcesSummary1\">Summary</h4><p>The summary table lists the resources that are part of this configuration, and for each resource it lists:</p><ul><li>The relevant profiles (if any)</li><li>The interactions supported by each resource (<b><span class=\"bg-info\">R</span></b>ead, <b><span class=\"bg-info\">S</span></b>earch, <b><span class=\"bg-info\">U</span></b>pdate, and <b><span class=\"bg-info\">C</span></b>reate, are always shown, while <b><span class=\"bg-info\">VR</span></b>ead, <b><span class=\"bg-info\">P</span></b>atch, <b><span class=\"bg-info\">D</span></b>elete, <b><span class=\"bg-info\">H</span></b>istory on <b><span class=\"bg-info\">I</span></b>nstance, or <b><span class=\"bg-info\">H</span></b>istory on <b><span class=\"bg-info\">T</span></b>ype are only present if at least one of the resources has support for them.</li><li><span>The required, recommended, and some optional search parameters (if any). </span></li><li>The linked resources enabled for <code>_include</code></li><li>The other resources enabled for <code>_revinclude</code></li><li>The operations on the resource (if any)</li></ul><div class=\"table-responsive\"><table class=\"table table-condensed table-hover\"><thead><tr><th><b>Resource Type</b></th><th><b>Profile</b></th><th class=\"text-center\"><b title=\"GET a resource (read interaction)\">R</b></th><th class=\"text-center\"><b title=\"GET all set of resources of the type (search interaction)\">S</b></th><th class=\"text-center\"><b title=\"PUT a new resource version (update interaction)\">U</b></th><th class=\"text-center\"><b title=\"POST a new resource (create interaction)\">C</b></th><th><b title=\"Required and recommended search parameters\">Searches</b></th><th><code><b>_include</b></code></th><th><code><b>_revinclude</b></code></th><th><b>Operations</b></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><a href=\"#Composition1-1\">Composition</a></td><td>Supported Profiles<br/>  <a href=\"StructureDefinition-ems-composition.html\">EMS Patient Care Report (PCR)</a></td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td>patient, date</td><td/><td/><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#Patient1-2\">Patient</a></td><td>Supported Profiles<br/>  <a href=\"StructureDefinition-ems-patient.html\">EMS Patient</a></td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td>identifier, birthdate, name</td><td/><td/><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#Encounter1-3\">Encounter</a></td><td>Supported Profiles<br/>  <a href=\"StructureDefinition-ems-encounter.html\">EMS Encounter</a></td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td>patient, date, identifier</td><td/><td/><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#Condition1-4\">Condition</a></td><td>Supported Profiles<br/>  <a href=\"StructureDefinition-ems-condition.html\">EMS Condition</a><br/>  <a href=\"StructureDefinition-ems-condition-arrest.html\">EMS Cardiac Arrest Condition</a></td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td>patient, encounter</td><td/><td/><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#Observation1-5\">Observation</a></td><td>Supported Profiles<br/>  <a href=\"StructureDefinition-ems-observation-vitalsigns.html\">EMS Vital Signs Observation</a><br/>  <a href=\"StructureDefinition-ems-observation-bp.html\">EMS Blood Pressure Observation</a><br/>  <a href=\"StructureDefinition-ems-observation-gcs.html\">EMS Glasgow Coma Score (GCS) Panel</a><br/>  <a href=\"StructureDefinition-ems-observation-exam.html\">EMS Physical Exam Observation</a><br/>  <a href=\"StructureDefinition-ems-observation-airway.html\">EMS Airway Management Observation</a><br/>  <a href=\"StructureDefinition-ems-observation-labs.html\">EMS Lab and Imaging Observation</a><br/>  <a href=\"StructureDefinition-ems-observation-outcome.html\">EMS Outcome Observation</a></td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td>patient, encounter, category, code, date</td><td/><td/><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#Procedure1-6\">Procedure</a></td><td>Supported Profiles<br/>  <a href=\"StructureDefinition-ems-procedure.html\">EMS Procedure</a></td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td>patient, encounter</td><td/><td/><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#MedicationAdministration1-7\">MedicationAdministration</a></td><td>Supported Profiles<br/>  <a href=\"StructureDefinition-ems-medicationadministration.html\">EMS Medication Administration</a></td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td>patient, context</td><td/><td/><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#AllergyIntolerance1-8\">AllergyIntolerance</a></td><td>Supported Profiles<br/>  <a href=\"StructureDefinition-ems-allergyintolerance.html\">EMS AllergyIntolerance</a></td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td>patient</td><td/><td/><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#Location1-9\">Location</a></td><td>Supported Profiles<br/>  <a href=\"StructureDefinition-ems-location-scene.html\">EMS Scene Location</a><br/>  <a href=\"StructureDefinition-ems-location-destination.html\">EMS Destination Location</a></td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td>name</td><td/><td/><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#Organization1-10\">Organization</a></td><td>Supported Profiles<br/>  <a href=\"StructureDefinition-ems-organization.html\">EMS Organization</a></td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td>identifier</td><td/><td/><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#Practitioner1-11\">Practitioner</a></td><td>Supported Profiles<br/>  <a href=\"StructureDefinition-ems-practitioner.html\">EMS Practitioner</a></td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-cente